Groupe de 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FCD9FDF5FB303128" authority="Mez" authorityName="Mez" box="[835,1178,532,559]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="robustum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FCD9FDF5FBC93128" bold="true" box="[835,1123,532,559]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">Tapeinosperma robustum</emphasis>
Mez
</taxonomicName>
</heading>
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
<subSubSection id="2BF24ACA1F78FF83FD3FFDB4FC413640" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" type="description">
<paragraph id="635719411F78FF83FD3FFDB4FC91316A" blockId="51.[674,1212,597,1351]" box="[677,827,597,623]" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">DESCRIPTION</paragraph>
<paragraph id="635719411F78FF83FD3FFD95FC413640" blockId="51.[674,1212,597,1351]" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">
Arbustes (
<quantity id="A410B4A41F78FF83FC8BFD95FCF83189" box="[785,850,628,654]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="2.0" metricValueMax="3.0" metricValueMin="1.0" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" unit="m" value="2.0" valueMax="3.0" valueMin="1.0">1-3 m</quantity>
) ou, parfois, petits arbres (jusqu’à 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F78FF83FD3FFD72FD7931A9" box="[677,723,659,686]" metricMagnitude="0" metricUnit="m" metricValue="9.0" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" unit="m" value="9.0">9 m</quantity>
). Feuilles à limbe parcheminé, le plus souvent coriace, subelliptique à oblancéolé, arrondi ou obtus au sommet, arrondi ou en coin ± largement ouvert vers la base,de dimensions moyennes (9-12× 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F78FF83FBF2FD13FB1B300A" box="[1128,1201,754,781]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.5" metricValueMax="6.0" metricValueMin="3.0" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" unit="cm" value="4.5" valueMax="6.0" valueMin="3.0">3-6 cm</quantity>
) à grandes (25-30 × 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F78FF83FCFFFCF3FC15302A" box="[869,959,786,813]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" metricValueMax="1.3" metricValueMin="0.7" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" unit="cm" value="10.0" valueMax="13.0" valueMin="7.0">7-13 cm</quantity>
), à pétiole généralement bien dégagé,long de(0,5-)1 à plusieurs cm, absent ou presque cependant dans le cas de 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FC75FCB3FBCC306C" authority="Schmid, 2012" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[1007,1126,849,875]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="kaalaense" status="sp.nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FC75FCB3FBCC306C" box="[1007,1126,849,875]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">T.kaalaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F78FF83FBF0FCB3FB12306B" box="[1130,1208,850,876]" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" rank="species">sp.nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
Inflorescences terminales sur des rameaux normaux ou sur des rameaux spéciaux, dressés, généralement nus vers la base, avec des feuilles de dimensions réduites, sous-jacentes aux inflorescences. Panicules 1-2fois ramifiées (parfois racèmes chez 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FBB9FC10FCB0372E" authority="M.Schmid" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="boulindaense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FBB9FC10FB13370D" box="[1059,1209,1008,1034]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">T.boulindaense</emphasis>
M.Schmid
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F78FF83FCBDFBF1FC2A372D" box="[807,896,1040,1066]" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
), généralement plus courtes que les feuilles, à axes non verruqueux, mais, dans certaines espèces (
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FCF6FBB1FB8F376E" authority="Mez" authorityName="Mez" box="[876,1061,1103,1129]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="deflexum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FCF6FBB1FC43376E" box="[876,1001,1103,1129]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">T. deflexum</emphasis>
Mez
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FBABFBB1FB18376E" box="[1073,1202,1103,1129]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="robustum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FBABFBB1FB18376E" box="[1073,1202,1103,1129]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">T. robustum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FD3FFB8EFCE6378E" authority="Mez" authorityName="Mez" box="[677,844,1134,1161]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubidum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FD3FFB8EFCBD378F" box="[677,791,1134,1160]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">T. rubidum</emphasis>
Mez
</taxonomicName>
), à pubescence rase ± discrète.Fleurs de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F78FF83FD5AFB6FFC8737AE" box="[704,813,1166,1193]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="3.25" metricValueMax="4.0" metricValueMin="2.5" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" unit="mm" value="3.25" valueMax="4.0" valueMin="2.5">2,5-4 mm</quantity>
, subsessiles (
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FC2AFB6EFB1937AF" authority="M.Schmid" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[944,1203,1166,1192]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="poueboense" status="sp.nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FC2AFB6EFB9337AF" box="[944,1081,1166,1192]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">T. poueboense</emphasis>
M.Schmid
</taxonomicName>
, 
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F78FF83FD3FFB4FFD5937CF" box="[677,755,1198,1224]" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" rank="species">sp.nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
, 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FD60FB4EFCC137CF" box="[762,875,1198,1224]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="rubidum">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FD60FB4EFCC137CF" box="[762,875,1198,1224]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">T.rubidum</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
), ou à pédicelle long de 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F78FF83FBC3FB4FFB1037CF" box="[1113,1210,1198,1224]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="6.0" metricValueMax="10.0" metricValueMin="2.0" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" unit="mm" value="6.0" valueMax="10.0" valueMin="2.0">2-10 mm</quantity>
(fleurs plus grandes et pédicelles atteignant 
<quantity id="A410B4A41F78FF83FBF2FB2CFB1D37EF" box="[1128,1207,1229,1256]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.5" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" unit="mm" value="15.0">15 mm</quantity>
chez 
<taxonomicName id="A4E862C21F78FF83FD44FB0FFC2C3600" authority="Schmid, 2012" authorityName="M. Schmid" authorityYear="2012" box="[734,902,1261,1287]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Primulaceae" genus="Tapeinosperma" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ericales" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="boulindaense" status="sp. nov.">
<emphasis id="519CC5531F78FF83FD44FB0FFC2C3600" box="[734,902,1261,1287]" italics="true" pageId="51" pageNumber="330">T. boulindaense</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<taxonomicNameLabel id="4AAF78281F78FF83FC14FB0FFC42360F" box="[910,1000,1262,1288]" pageId="51" pageNumber="330" rank="species">sp. nov.</taxonomicNameLabel>
). Fruits globuleux, subsphériques, ou un peu comprimés axialement, de 8-15(-20) mm de diamètre.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</treatment>
